name: Survivor
overview: Hungarian version of the reality contest where a group of castaways split between two or more “Tribes” are taken to a remote isolated location and are forced to live off the land with meager supplies. Frequent physical challenges are used to pit the tribes against each other for rewards, such as food or luxuries, or for “Immunity”, forcing the other tribe to attend “Tribal Council”, where they must vote off one of their players.
